    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Puzzles, usually made of wood and intended for young children, where cut-out shapes must be placed in a matching hole. Often the puzzle pieces have knobs or pegs that make them easier to grasp.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
